author: Jon Fingas
title: Self-driving shuttles are ferrying COVID-19 tests at a Florida clinic
description: Drive-thru COVID-19 tests are only as safe and quick as the systems used to put those tests in the hands of clinics, and a new initiative in Jacksonville, Florida might just improve that weak link.
